      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;antipaladin 1, mesmerist 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a slit purse)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one creature<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You awaken a sudden criminal impulse in the target, compelling it to commit a criminal act as if affected by the <i>crime wave</i> spell.</p>\n</div>\n",
